sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Shiny UI
    participant Server (Orchestrator)
    participant Polars (Wrangler)
    participant Plotnine (Viz Factory)

    User->>Shiny UI: Updates Slider (e.g. Year > 2002)
    Shiny UI->>Server: Sends filter dictionary: {"Year": ">2002"}
    Server->>Polars: Appends condition to LazyFrame plan and collects()
    Polars-->>Server: Returns tiny filtered DataFrame in memory
    Server->>Plotnine: Passes DataFrame & Config mapping
    Plotnine-->>Server: Generates updated Static Plot
    Server-->>Shiny UI: Returns new image
    Shiny UI-->>User: Displays updated plot
